title.rendered: Luxurious Apartment For Sale In Vasant Vihar

content.rendered:
We are delighted to introduce to the market this splendid four-bedroom luxury apartment located in an exclusive housing locality of Vasant Vihar. This 600sqyds attractive, spacious, and plush home boasts 4 tidy & spacious bedrooms with adjoining top-notch bathrooms & spacious balconies, and a separate drawing dining room with grandeur interiors and furniture. a splendid, modern, & fully loaded kitchen with high-end functional appliances, and an automatic Schindler lift & stilt car parking space.
♕4BHK
♕600 Sqyds
♕3200sqft
♕For Sale
♕Corner Building
♕Stilt Parking
♕Grandeur Interiors
♕Posh Location
♕Secured Neighbourhood
📞 Call On 9818312077 For Site Visit or More Information
Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
Checkout Our Other Listings
